  "description": "High-range CO₂ concentration sensing tile based on the Sensirion STC31-C thermal conductivity sensor. Measures CO₂ from 0 to 100 vol% with accuracy down to ±0.2 vol%, supporting both low-noise and low-cross-sensitivity measurement modes. Features automatic self-calibration and forced recalibration for long-term stability.  Suited for gas leak detection, breath analysis, capnography, and industrial CO₂ monitoring.\n",
